  "remarks": "Defence Industries Organisation (DIO) was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: an entity involved in nuclear programme. Overarching MODAFL-controlled entity, some of whose subordinates have been involved in the centrifuge programme making components, and in the missile programme. The Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
